03:47.654 --> 03:49.255
So read it to him then.

03:49.289 --> 03:51.257
I always pre-read it

03:51.291 --> 03:52.591
and circle the articles I think he'll like

03:52.626 --> 03:55.428
because time is an issue
at his age and he gets really upset

03:55.462 --> 03:57.530
if he falls asleep before
I get to Gail Collins.

03:57.564 --> 03:59.532
